quran[5{c,v,t}:
42,11,asmano aur zameen ka peda karne wala ( wohi hai ). isi ne tumahray liye tumhari hi jins ke jore banaye aur charpayon ke bhi jore ( banaye aur ) isi tareeq par tum ko phelata rehta hai. is jaisi koi cheez nahi. aur woh daikhta santa hai
42,12,asmano aur zameen ki knjyan isi ke haath mein hain. woh jis ke liye chahta hai rizaq farakh kardaita hai ( aur jis ke liye chahta hai ) tang kardaita hai. be shak woh har cheez se waaqif hai
42,13,isi ne tumahray liye deen ka wohi rasta muqarrarkiya jis ( ke ikhtiyar karne ka ) Nooh ko hukum diya tha aur jis ki ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tumhari taraf wahi bhaije hai aur jis ka ibrahim aur moose aur eesa ko hukum diya tha ( woh yeh ) ke deen ko qaim rakhna aur is mein phoot nah daalna. jis cheez ki taraf tum mushrikon ko bulatay ho woh un ko dushwaar guzarti hai. allah jis ko chahta hai apni bargaah ka bargzida karleta hai aur jo is ki taraf rujoo kere usay apni taraf rasta dikha deta hai
42,14,aur yeh log jo allag allag hue hain to ilm ( haq ) aa Chuknay ke baad aapas ki zid se ( hue hain ). aur agar tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se aik waqt muqarrar taq ke liye baat nah thehr chuki hoti to un mein faisla kardiya jata. aur jo log un ke baad ( khuda ki ) kitaab ke waris hue woh is ( ki taraf ) se shubhay ki uljan mein ( phansay hue ) hain
42,15,to ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) isi ( deen ki ) taraf ( logon ko ) bulatay rehna aur jaissa tum ko hukum howa hai ( isi par ) qaim rehna. aur un ki khawahishon ki pairwi nah karna. aur keh do ke jo kitaab khuda ne nazil farmai hai mein is par imaan rakhta hon. aur mujhe hukum howa hai ke tum mein insaaf karoon. khuda hi hamara aur tumhara perwar-digaar hai. hum ko hamaray aamaal ( ka badla miley ga ) aur tum ko tumahray aamaal ka. hum mein aur tum mein kuch behas o takraar nahi. khuda hum ( sab ) ko akatha kere ga. aur isi ki taraf lout kar jana hai
